Anglican Church of Kenya Archbishop Jackson ole Sapit has urged the clergy to preach unity. Addressing congregants at St Stephens ACK Cathedral in Milimani yesterday, Mr Sapit said he was disturbed by divisive opinions from the clergy over certain matters affecting the country. ALSO READ:

